---
import ChadLogo from './ChadLogo.astro';
---
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Decorative background elements -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-cyber-cyan/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center space-y-8">
        <div class="reveal mb-8">
            <ChadLogo />
        </div>
        
        <div class="reveal inline-block bg-cyber-pink/10 text-cyber-pink font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-cyber-pink/20 mb-4 animate-pulse">
            ‚ö†Ô∏è WARNING: High Performance Zone
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="reveal text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white leading-[0.9] impact">
            STOP CODING LIKE <br>
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyber-cyan to-blue-500">A MID-TIER DEV</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="reveal text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Standard Git setups are high-latency and low-aesthetic. Embrace the <span class="text-cyber-cyan font-bold">Bare Hub Architecture</span>. 
            Decouple your engine from your muscle. Work on five branches at once. Zero bloat. 100% Gains.
        </p>
        
        <div class="reveal flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 pt-8">
            <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/#protocol`} class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 font-impact text-2xl tracking-widest text-cyber-bg bg-cyber-cyan transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">
                INITIALIZE PROTOCOL
                <div class="absolute -inset-1 border border-white/20 -z-10 group-hover:-inset-2 transition-all"></div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-20">
            <div class="reveal bg-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 neon-box backdrop-blur-sm group hover:border-cyber-cyan transition-colors">
                <div class="text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">‚ö°</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 impact">Instant Switching</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">No more checkout delays. Branches are dedicated directories. Just change path.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal bg-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 neon-box backdrop-blur-sm group hover:border-cyber-pink transition-colors">
                <div class="text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">üí™</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 impact">Parallel Muscle</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Run heavy tests on `main` while simultaneously coding on `feature-x`.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal bg-slate-800/50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 neon-box backdrop-blur-sm group hover:border-cyber-green transition-colors">
                <div class="text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">üßπ</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 impact">Zero Clutter</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Keep your root directory clean. The Git engine stays hidden in `.bare`.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
